➜口红在多高温度下会融化？
http://www.sohu.com/a/291180813_99953098	5038
<p>口红在多少度会融化？</p>
<p>测试方法：按照图片顺序阅读，首先将高大上的<strong>高低温试验箱</strong>温度设定值设为60℃，观察下口红的颜色与形状，然后点击设备开始运行，时间为一小时。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190124/2462841531e54ec9b1c44487009c3217.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190124/d9922ab3af8d4d898be798d27453b191.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190124/d1872972885b4ce3b0f722fbaa8860c3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
